betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Before starting your journey, there are some things you should know.

There are skyblock related mods in this modpack
Some recipes were heavily changed. Remember: this is not supposed to be an easy pack
There is progression in this pack, meaning, you might to follow a certain order to get to your target.
The mobs are also more difficult in this pack and you only start with 8 hearts. You can get more hearts by killing mobs.
Production and Usage of ForgeEnergy mods heavily changed.

That about it

Happy Crafting,
-Extended Team

A place to store all the experience!

Here it all starts!

The name of the quests in this chapter correspond to the 1.7.10 equivalent, Magical Crops, of which this chapter was based of.

The way Refined Storage works in this pack is different than your are expecting.

Refined Storage is meant to replace the 'old' Inventory Panel from Ender IO from the 1.7.10 version of this pack to help with some of the tedious crafts (through the crafting grid) but without being too op for the stage of the game. Most of the communication with the "outside world" is locked until you unlock AE2. Then, you can continue doing RS (although you are going to need AE2 components for the RS crafts) or change to AE2.

Also, AE2 channels are enabled in this pack.
